The hotel staff was all fantastic, we had great service at the concierge, front desk, lounge, bell desk, and restaurant.	The housekeeping staff was invisible yet they always cleaned our room whenever we left the room, which is the way it should be.	The front desk staff addressed me by name every time I passed the desk, and always with a smile.	The hotel made a few dinner reservations for us and we always got an excellent table with great wait staff.